author: Andrew Mark Miller
title: Staggering Statistic About Liberal Protesters Reveals Everything You Need to Know…
text:
06:11pm February 7, 2017   
The situation that unfolded in Berkeley last week when Milo attempted to make a speech is one of the most embarrassing displays of intolerance you will ever see. 
The liberal left has made it abundantly clear that conservatives in 2017 aren’t even allowed to open their mouths to speak on a college campus. 
That’s an alarming development from a group who pretends to pride themselves on “tolerance”. 
Who are these protesters? What’s the story behind the mask? 
Check out these fun little statistics about “antifascist” protesters… 
Research found that 92% of those suspected of violent crimes at Left-leaning demonstrations still share their home with their parents. 84% are male
